text_zh: 面对新的挑战时，你的第一反应是什么？
text_en: When facing new challenges, what is your first reaction?
option_a_zh: 兴奋地接受挑战，追求突破
option_a_en: Excitedly accept the challenge and pursue breakthroughs
option_b_zh: 仔细评估风险，确保安全
option_b_en: Carefully assess risks to ensure safety
option_d_en: Collaborate with others to tackle it together

text_zh: 什么最能激发你的内在动力？
text_en: What most motivates you internally?
option_a_en: Gaining recognition and sense of achievement

text_zh: 当你设定目标时，什么因素最重要？
text_en: When setting goals, what factor is most important?
option_a_zh: 目标的挑战性和成就感
option_b_zh: 目标的可实现性和安全性
option_c_zh: 目标的创新性和突破性
option_d_zh: 目标对他人的积极影响

text_zh: 在追求成功的过程中，你最看重什么？
text_en: In pursuing success, what do you value most?

text_zh: 你认为真正的成功是什么？
text_en: What do you think true success is?
option_a_en: Surpassing others and reaching the peak

text_zh: 面对失败时，你的态度是？
text_en: What is your attitude when facing failure?
option_c_en: Learn from it and find new methods

text_zh: 在做重要决定时，你最依赖什么？
text_en: When making important decisions, what do you rely on most?

text_zh: 你最害怕失去什么？
text_en: What are you most afraid of losing?

text_zh: 什么样的环境让你感到最舒适？
text_en: What kind of environment makes you feel most comfortable?

text_zh: 在不确定的情况下，你倾向于？
text_en: In uncertain situations, you tend to?
option_a_en: Take active action and create opportunities
option_b_en: Observe carefully and wait for timing
option_c_en: Be flexible and adapt as needed

text_zh: 你对变化的态度是？
text_en: What is your attitude towards change?
option_b_en: Adapt to change while maintaining stability

text_zh: 在压力下，你的反应是？
text_en: Under pressure, your reaction is?

text_zh: 在社交场合中，你更倾向于？
text_en: In social situations, you tend to?
option_b_en: Observe others and adapt to environment

text_zh: 你最看重友谊中的什么？
text_en: What do you value most in friendship?

text_zh: 在团队合作中，你最关注什么？
text_en: In teamwork, what do you focus on most?
option_d_zh: 团队成员的感受和需求

text_zh: 当朋友需要帮助时，你会？
text_en: When friends need help, you will?
option_a_en: Take immediate action to solve problems
option_c_en: Think innovatively and find new methods
option_d_en: Listen patiently and provide emotional support

text_zh: 你认为理想的人际关系是？
text_en: What do you think ideal interpersonal relationships are?

text_zh: 在处理人际冲突时，你的方式是？
text_en: When dealing with interpersonal conflicts, your approach is?

text_zh: 你最看重的自由是什么？
text_en: What freedom do you value most?

text_zh: 在工作中，你最希望拥有什么？
text_en: At work, what do you most hope to have?

text_zh: 你对规则和制度的态度是？
text_en: What is your attitude towards rules and systems?
option_b_en: Apply flexibly and adapt to situations
option_c_en: Innovate and improve for better results

text_zh: 在学习新知识时，你偏好？
text_en: When learning new knowledge, you prefer?

text_zh: 你理想的生活状态是？
text_en: What is your ideal life state?
option_b_en: Free and easy, following one's heart

text_zh: 面对权威时，你的态度是？
text_en: What is your attitude when facing authority?

text_zh: 你的核心价值观是什么？
text_en: What are your core values?

text_zh: 什么最能体现你的人生意义？
text_en: What best reflects the meaning of your life?
option_a_en: Achieve career success and gain recognition
option_b_en: Deep thinking and understanding the world

text_zh: 在人生的十字路口，你如何选择？
text_en: At life's crossroads, how do you choose?
option_a_zh: 选择最有挑战性的道路
option_b_zh: 选择最灵活自由的道路
option_b_en: Choose the most flexible and free path
option_c_zh: 选择最深思熟虑的道路
option_d_zh: 选择最温暖人心的道路

text_zh: 你认为成功的人生需要什么？
text_en: What do you think a successful life needs?

text_zh: 面对人生的不确定性，你的态度是？
text_en: What is your attitude towards life's uncertainties?
option_a_en: Actively respond and turn crisis into opportunity
option_b_en: Accept reality and let nature take its course

text_zh: 你希望别人如何记住你？
text_en: How do you want others to remember you?

text_zh: 在团队中，你通常扮演什么角色？
text_en: What role do you usually play in a team?

text_zh: 面对冲突时，你的典型反应是？
text_en: What is your typical reaction when facing conflicts?
option_a_en: Face it directly and seek solutions
option_d_en: Listen to all parties and seek consensus

text_zh: 在工作中，你更喜欢如何与他人互动？
text_en: How do you prefer to interact with others at work?

text_zh: 当需要做出群体决策时，你倾向于？
text_en: When group decisions need to be made, you tend to?
option_a_en: Lead the discussion and decision-making process

text_zh: 在项目管理中，你最注重什么？
text_en: In project management, what do you focus on most?

text_zh: 面对团队成员的不同意见时，你会？
text_en: When facing different opinions from team members, you will?
option_a_zh: 坚持自己的判断和决定
option_a_en: Stick to your own judgment and decisions

text_zh: 在合作中，你最看重什么？
text_en: In cooperation, what do you value most?
option_a_en: Clear division of labor and responsibilities

text_zh: 当团队遇到困难时，你的反应是？
text_en: When the team encounters difficulties, your reaction is?
option_a_zh: 分析问题，寻找解决方案
option_b_en: Encourage the team and maintain morale

text_zh: 在跨部门协作中，你倾向于？
text_en: In cross-departmental collaboration, you tend to?
option_a_zh: 建立标准化的协作流程
option_b_zh: 灵活适应不同部门文化
option_b_en: Flexibly adapt to different departmental cultures
option_d_en: Deeply understand the needs of each department

text_zh: 处理团队内部矛盾时，你会？
text_en: When dealing with internal team conflicts, you will?
option_d_en: Analyze deeply and find the root cause

text_zh: 在资源分配中，你的原则是？
text_en: What is your principle in resource allocation?
option_a_en: Allocate according to contribution and ability

text_zh: 评价团队成功的标准是什么？
text_en: What is the standard for evaluating team success?

text_zh: 在表达观点时，你更倾向于？
text_en: When expressing your views, you tend to?
option_a_en: Direct and clear, concise and to the point
option_d_zh: 温和委婉，考虑他人感受
option_d_en: Gentle and tactful, considering others' feelings

text_zh: 面对不同观点时，你的反应是？
text_en: What is your reaction when facing different viewpoints?
option_b_en: Be open and flexible in adjustment

text_zh: 在说服他人时，你依赖什么？
text_en: When persuading others, what do you rely on?

text_zh: 处理信息时，你更注重什么？
text_en: When processing information, what do you focus on more?
option_a_zh: 信息的准确性和可靠性
option_b_zh: 信息的实用性和相关性
option_c_zh: 信息的新颖性和创新性

text_zh: 在倾听他人时，你最关注什么？
text_en: When listening to others, what do you focus on most?

text_zh: 在会议讨论中，你的角色通常是？
text_en: What is your usual role in meeting discussions?
option_a_en: Lead the agenda and control the pace
option_b_en: Enliven the atmosphere and promote participation

text_zh: 面对变化时，你的第一反应是？
text_en: What is your first reaction when facing change?
option_c_en: Analyze deeply and understand the essence

text_zh: 在不熟悉的环境中，你会？
text_en: In an unfamiliar environment, you will?

text_zh: 学习新技能时，你的方法是？
text_en: What is your method when learning new skills?
option_a_en: Learn through practice, learning by doing
option_b_en: Systematic learning and building a solid foundation

text_zh: 处理突发事件时，你倾向于？
text_en: When dealing with emergencies, you tend to?
option_a_en: Make quick decisions and take immediate action

text_zh: 面对技术更新时，你的态度是？
text_en: What is your attitude when facing technological updates?
option_d_en: Focus on impact and balance pros and cons

text_zh: 在多任务处理中，你的策略是？
text_en: What is your strategy in multitasking?
option_a_en: Prioritize and complete one by one
option_b_en: Process in parallel and switch flexibly
option_d_en: Team division of labor and collaborative completion

text_zh: 在压力下工作时，你的表现如何？
text_en: How do you perform when working under pressure?

text_zh: 评估工作成果时，你最看重什么？
text_en: When evaluating work results, what do you value most?

text_zh: 在职业发展中，你的策略是？
text_en: What is your strategy in career development?
option_a_zh: 设定明确目标，努力攀登
option_a_en: Set clear goals and strive to climb
option_b_en: Maintain flexibility and adapt to change
option_c_en: Deep specialization and become an expert

text_zh: 在团队协作中，你的贡献通常是？
text_en: What is your usual contribution in team collaboration?
option_c_en: Innovative thinking and proposing new ideas

text_zh: 面对工作挫折时，你的应对方式是？
text_en: How do you cope when facing work setbacks?

text_zh: 在工作中，你最希望获得什么样的反馈？
text_en: What kind of feedback do you most hope to receive at work?
